---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Opening hours
intro: "We're open Monday to Friday. Here are our full opening hours and what to do when we're closed."
description: "Opening hours for Scoonie Medical Practice — Monday to Friday 8am to 6pm, with out-of-hours guidance."
breadcrumb:
  - label: About us
    url: /about/
  - label: Opening hours
---

<div class="max-w-2xl">

  <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8">
    <table class="hours-table w-full" aria-label="Surgery opening hours">
      <caption class="sr-only">Opening hours for Scoonie Medical Practice</caption>
      <thead class="bg-brand-light">
        <tr>
          <th scope="col" class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-neutral-dark">Day</th>
          <th scope="col" class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-neutral-dark">Hours</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for row in site.openingHours %}
        <tr data-day="{{ row.day }}" class="border-t border-gray-100">
          <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium">{{ row.day }}</td>
          <td class="py-3 px-4">
            {% if row.open %}
              {{ row.open }} – {{ row.close }}
            {% else %}
              <span class="text-neutral-mid">Closed</span>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="prose-content">
    <h2>Telephone lines</h2>
    <p>Telephone lines open from 08:00. If you call and our lines are busy, please hold or call back. We aim to answer all calls as quickly as possible.</p>

    <h2>Public holidays</h2>
    <p>We are closed on Scottish public holidays. Upcoming closure dates:</p>
    <ul>
      {% for closure in site.plannedClosures %}
        {% if "Protected Learning Time" not in closure.reason %}
      <li>{{ closure.date }} — {{ closure.reason }}</li>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <h2>Protected Learning Time (PLT)</h2>
    <p>The practice will close early at <strong>1:00pm</strong> on the following dates for Protected Learning Time (PLT) sessions. For urgent medical advice after 1pm on these days, please call NHS 24 on <a href="tel:111">111</a>.</p>
    <ul>
      {% for closure in site.plannedClosures %}
        {% if "Protected Learning Time" in closure.reason %}
      <li>{{ closure.date }}{% if closure.details %} — {{ closure.details }}{% endif %}</li>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <h2>Out of hours</h2>
    <p>When we're closed, you can get urgent medical advice by calling <a href="tel:111" class="font-semibold">NHS 24 on 111</a>, available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>
    <p>For life-threatening emergencies, always call <a href="tel:999" class="font-semibold text-alert-urgent">999</a>.</p>
  </div>

</div>
